    <fr:title text="Maps preserving constructible sets">Maps preserving constructible sets</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
  We say a map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Y \to  X]]></fr:tex> <html:em>preserves <fr:link href="/topl-F1KS/" title="Constructible topology" uri="https://charloced.github.io/topl-F1KS/" display-uri="topl-F1KS" type="local">constructible sets</fr:link></html:em> if the image of a constructible subsets of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Y]]></fr:tex> is again constructible.
</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
